<p><strong>SCP-3941：</strong>大隐遁<br />
<strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3337265); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3337265&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663820" alt="Tufto" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3337265)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3337265); return false;">Tufto</a></span>，使用原账号发表。更多作品可见<a href="/tufto-personnel-file">此处</a>。<br />
<strong>译者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/varitas096" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3335543); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3335543&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663820" alt="varitas096" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3335543)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/varitas096" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3335543); return false;">varitas096</a></span><br />
<strong>插图：</strong>见于<a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Double_knock_old_door_(2624799098).jpg">此处</a>，遵照CC协议。</p>
